@DATABASE "Dizzy"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - D - Dizzy"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - D
                   ====================================

                                   Dizzy
                                   =====


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(62789,255)"}          62789,x (x = 1-255)
@{"Walk Speed = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(59644,4)"}          62789,x (x = 1-7)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(62745,0)"}          62745,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(54216,0)"}          54216,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         With the "Walk Spped" POKE, the default setting is 4
                         (just press the button), 1= Fast, 7= Slow.

                         I would advise NOT using the Immunity POKE as there
                         are some parts of the game that you can sink through
                         and end up in "limbo" and have to abort the game :(

                         Rastan.
@endnode
